<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="policy-header">
    <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="policy-title">Refund &amp; Return Policy</h1>
    <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-body">

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>30-Day Guarantee</h2>
      <p>We stand behind the ritual. If you do the 5-minute ritual every morning for 30 days and don't see a difference, contact us and we'll refund you in full — no questions asked.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Your EU Right of Withdrawal</h2>
      <p>As a customer in Belgium and the EU, you have the legal right to cancel your order within <strong>14 days</strong> of receiving your goods, without giving any reason. This is your statutory right under EU Directive 2011/83/EU.</p>
      <p>To exercise your right of withdrawal, contact us at <a href="mailto:byrituel@yahoo.com">byrituel@yahoo.com</a> within 14 days of delivery. You then have another 14 days to return the item.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Return Conditions</h2>
      <p>To be eligible for a return:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Items must be unused and in their original condition</li>
        <li>Items must be returned within 14 days of your cancellation notice</li>
        <li>You are responsible for return shipping costs unless the item is defective or incorrect</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not accept returns on used skincare products (rosehip oil) for hygiene reasons, unless the product is defective.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Damaged or Incorrect Items</h2>
      <p>If your order arrives damaged or you received the wrong item, contact us within 7 days of delivery at <a href="mailto:byrituel@yahoo.com">byrituel@yahoo.com</a> with a photo. We will send a replacement or issue a full refund at no cost to you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Refund Processing</h2>
      <p>Once your return is received and inspected, we will notify you by email. Approved refunds are processed within <strong>7 business days</strong> to your original payment method. Your bank may take additional time to post the refund.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For any return or refund request: <a href="mailto:byrituel@yahoo.com">byrituel@yahoo.com</a></p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

